<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.2.4">
<l>uṇṇumnā ḷillai yuṟakkamun tāṉillai</l>
<l>peṇmaiyuñ cāla niṟaintilaḷ pētaitāṉ</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṉūr kaṇṇa purantoḻuṅ kārkkaṭal</l>
<l>vaṇṇarmē leṇṇa mivaṭkitu veṉkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is not a day that [she] eats; there is no sleep [at night].</l>
<l>She is not full of feminine wiles; she is simple girl.</l>
<l>She worships Kaṇṇaṉ’s city, Kaṇṇapuram;</l>
<l>For her, thoughts are [only] of the sea-hued one. What is this?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
